description:
This market will resolve to the contestant or group who wins Sing for Greece 2026.

If at any point it is impossible for the listed candidate to win Sing for Greece 2026 based on the rules of the competition (i.e. they are eliminated), this market may immediately resolve to "No".

If no winner is announced by March 31, 2026, 11:59 PM ET, this market will resolve "Other". All ties will be broken according to official Sing for Greece rules.

The primary resolution source for this market will be official information from Eurovision (https://eurovisionworld.com/national/greece/sing-for-greece-2026), including live footage of Sing for Greece 2026, however a consensus of credible reporting will suffice.
